JSONParser

public JSONParser(java.io.Reader reader,
                  boolean stopOnSocketTimeout)
Create a JSONParser for a given character-based input reader.

Parameters:
reader - The input reader
stopOnSocketTimeout - If true, the parser stops reading when a SocketTimeoutException is thrown by the input reader's read() method. If false, reading is continued if the parser is not signaled to stop.
